# ==============================================================================
# Gitignore Template for Developer Monorepo
# Setup for: Java, Spring Boot, Oracle SQL/PLSQL, VS Code, and JetBrains IDEs
# ==============================================================================

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 1. Global / Core System Rules
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Compiled/Binary OS files
Thumbs.db
dbjs.data
Desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
._*

# Log files and databases
*.log
*.sqlite

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 2. JetBrains IDEs (IntelliJ IDEA, DataGrip, etc.)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Covers project-specific configurations while preserving global/shared layouts
.idea/
*.iml
*.iws
*.ipr
out/
gen/

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 3. Visual Studio Code
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Exclude workspace configurations that shouldn't be shared across machines
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
.history/
*.code-workspace

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 4. Java Core & Build Automation Tools (Maven / Gradle)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Compiled Java artifacts
*.class
*.pyc
*.war
*.nar
*.ear
*.jar
*.zip
*.tar.gz
*.rar

# Maven build outputs
**/target/
pom.xml.tag
pom.xml.releaseBackup
pom.xml.next
pom.xml.versionsBackup
release.properties
dependency-reduced-pom.xml
buildNumber.properties
.mvn/timing.properties
.mvn/wrapper/.maven-wrapper.properties

# Gradle build outputs
**/.gradle/
**/build/
!**/src/main/**/build/
!**/src/test/**/build/

# Gradle Tooling and Wrappers
.gradletasknamecache
gradle-app.setting

# Crash logs
hs_err_pid*
replay_pid*

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 5. Spring Boot & Cloud Framework Framework Extensions
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Spring Boot application logs and local configurations
**/logs/
*.log.gz
**/help.md
**/.sts4-cache/

# Sensitive Runtime Properties (Prevent pushing real credentials)
**/application-dev.properties
**/application-local.properties
**/application-dev.yml
**/application-local.yml
**/application-*.properties
**/application-*.yml
!**/application.properties
!**/application.yml

# NetBeans specific overrides (if used transitively)
**/nbproject/private/
**/nbbuild/
**/dist/
**/nbdist/
**/.nb-gradle/

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 6. Oracle SQL, PL/SQL & Database Client Tooling
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# SQL Developer, DataGrip, and migration execution outputs
**/.sqlcli/
**/SQLDeveloper/
**/.datagrip/
*.sql.bak
*.txt.bak

# Local Environment Variables and Secrets (e.g., wallet locations, DB connections)
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
*.wallet
*.p12
*.jks
credentials.xml
connections.xml
jdbc.properties